{"id":276,"ayahs":[{"number":80,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ جَعَلَ لَكُم مِّنۢ بُيُوتِكُمْ سَكَنًۭا وَجَعَلَ لَكُم مِّن جُلُودِ ٱلْأَنْعَٰمِ بُيُوتًۭا تَسْتَخِفُّونَهَا يَوْمَ ظَعْنِكُمْ وَيَوْمَ إِقَامَتِكُمْ ۙ وَمِنْ أَصْوَافِهَا وَأَوْبَارِهَا وَأَشْعَارِهَآ أَثَٰثًۭا وَمَتَٰعًا إِلَىٰ حِينٍۢ","translation":"And God has given you [the ability to build] your houses as places of rest, and has endowed you with [the skill to make] dwellings out of the skins of animals - easy for you to handle when you travel and when you camp -and [to make] furnishings and goods for temporary use of their [rough] wool and their soft, furry wool and their hair.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1981.mp3","surahId":16,"words":[{"id":64080,"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","translation":"এবং আল্লাহ্‌","audioUrl":"wbw/016_080_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64081,"position":2,"arabic":"جَعَلَ","translation":"বানিয়েছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/016_080_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64082,"position":3,"arabic":"لَكُم","translation":"জন্যে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/016_080_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64083,"position":4,"arabic":"مِّنۢ","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_080_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64084,"position":5,"arabic":"بُيُوتِكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের ঘরগুলো","audioUrl":"wbw/016_080_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64085,"position":6,"arabic":"سَكَنًۭا","translation":"আবাসস্থল","audioUrl":"wbw/016_080_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64086,"position":7,"arabic":"وَجَعَلَ","translation":"ও বানিয়েছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/016_080_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64087,"position":8,"arabic":"لَكُم","translation":"জন্যে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/016_080_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64088,"position":9,"arabic":"مِّن","translation":"দিয়ে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_080_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64089,"position":10,"arabic":"جُلُودِ","translation":"চামড়াগুলোকে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_080_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64090,"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلْأَنْعَـٰمِ","translation":"গবাদিপশুর","audioUrl":"wbw/016_080_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64091,"position":12,"arabic":"بُيُوتًۭا","translation":"এমন ঘর","audioUrl":"wbw/016_080_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64092,"position":13,"arabic":"تَسْتَخِفُّونَهَا","translation":"তা তোমরা হালকা মনে করো","audioUrl":"wbw/016_080_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64093,"position":14,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","translation":"দিনে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_080_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64094,"position":15,"arabic":"ظَعْنِكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের ভ্রমনের","audioUrl":"wbw/016_080_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64095,"position":16,"arabic":"وَيَوْمَ","translation":"ও দিনে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_080_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64096,"position":17,"arabic":"إِقَامَتِكُمْ ۙ","translation":"তোমাদের অবস্থানের","audioUrl":"wbw/016_080_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64098,"position":18,"arabic":"وَمِنْ","translation":"এবং থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_080_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64099,"position":19,"arabic":"أَصْوَافِهَا","translation":"তার পশমগুলো","audioUrl":"wbw/016_080_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64100,"position":20,"arabic":"وَأَوْبَارِهَا","translation":"ও তার লোমগুলো","audioUrl":"wbw/016_080_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64101,"position":21,"arabic":"وَأَشْعَارِهَآ","translation":"ও তার চুলগুলো","audioUrl":"wbw/016_080_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64102,"position":22,"arabic":"أَثَـٰثًۭا","translation":"গৃহসামগ্রী","audioUrl":"wbw/016_080_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64103,"position":23,"arabic":"وَمَتَـٰعًا","translation":"ও ব্যবহার উপকরণ","audioUrl":"wbw/016_080_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64104,"position":24,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ","translation":"পর্যন্ত","audioUrl":"wbw/016_080_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64105,"position":25,"arabic":"حِينٍۢ","translation":"নির্দিষ্ট সময়","audioUrl":"wbw/016_080_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64106,"position":26,"arabic":"٨٠","translation":"(৮০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":81,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ جَعَلَ لَكُم مِّمَّا خَلَقَ ظِلَٰلًۭا وَجَعَلَ لَكُم مِّنَ ٱلْجِبَالِ أَكْنَٰنًۭا وَجَعَلَ لَكُمْ سَرَٰبِيلَ تَقِيكُمُ ٱلْحَرَّ وَسَرَٰبِيلَ تَقِيكُم بَأْسَكُمْ ۚ كَذَٰلِكَ يُتِمُّ نِعْمَتَهُۥ عَلَيْكُمْ لَعَلَّكُمْ تُسْلِمُونَ","translation":"And among the many objects of His creation, God has appointed for you [various] means of protection: thus, He has given you in the mountains places of shelter, and has endowed you with [the ability to make] garments to protect you from heat [and cold], as well as such garments as might protect you from your [mutual] violence. In this way does He bestow the full measure of His blessings on you, so that you might surrender yourselves unto Him.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1982.mp3","surahId":16,"words":[{"id":64568,"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","translation":"এবং আল্লাহ্‌","audioUrl":"wbw/016_081_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64569,"position":2,"arabic":"جَعَلَ","translation":"ব্যবস্থা করেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/016_081_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64570,"position":3,"arabic":"لَكُم","translation":"জন্যে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/016_081_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64571,"position":4,"arabic":"مِّمَّا","translation":"তা হ'তে যা","audioUrl":"wbw/016_081_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64572,"position":5,"arabic":"خَلَقَ","translation":"তিনি সৃষ্টি করেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/016_081_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64573,"position":6,"arabic":"ظِلَـٰلًۭا","translation":"ছায়াসমূহের","audioUrl":"wbw/016_081_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64574,"position":7,"arabic":"وَجَعَلَ","translation":"এবং বানিয়েছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/016_081_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64575,"position":8,"arabic":"لَكُم","translation":"জন্যে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/016_081_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64576,"position":9,"arabic":"مِّنَ","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_081_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64577,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلْجِبَالِ","translation":"পাহাড়সমূহের","audioUrl":"wbw/016_081_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64578,"position":11,"arabic":"أَكْنَـٰنًۭا","translation":"আশ্রয়স্থলসমূহ","audioUrl":"wbw/016_081_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64579,"position":12,"arabic":"وَجَعَلَ","translation":"এবং ব্যবস্থা করেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/016_081_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64580,"position":13,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","translation":"জন্যে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/016_081_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64581,"position":14,"arabic":"سَرَٰبِيلَ","translation":"পোশাকসমূহের","audioUrl":"wbw/016_081_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64582,"position":15,"arabic":"تَقِيكُمُ","translation":"রক্ষা করে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/016_081_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64583,"position":16,"arabic":"ٱلْحَرَّ","translation":"গরমে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_081_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64584,"position":17,"arabic":"وَسَرَٰبِيلَ","translation":"ও পোশাকসমূহ (বর্ম)","audioUrl":"wbw/016_081_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64585,"position":18,"arabic":"تَقِيكُم","translation":"রক্ষা করে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/016_081_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64586,"position":19,"arabic":"بَأْسَكُمْ ۚ","translation":"তোমাদের যুদ্ধে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_081_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64588,"position":20,"arabic":"كَذَٰلِكَ","translation":"এভাবে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_081_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64589,"position":21,"arabic":"يُتِمُّ","translation":"তিনি পূর্ণ করেন","audioUrl":"wbw/016_081_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64590,"position":22,"arabic":"نِعْمَتَهُۥ","translation":"অনুগ্রহ তাঁর","audioUrl":"wbw/016_081_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64591,"position":23,"arabic":"عَلَيْكُمْ","translation":"ওপর তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/016_081_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64592,"position":24,"arabic":"لَعَلَّكُمْ","translation":"সম্ভবত তোমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/016_081_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64593,"position":25,"arabic":"تُسْلِمُونَ","translation":"আত্নসমর্পণ করবে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_081_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64594,"position":26,"arabic":"٨١","translation":"(৮১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":82,"arabic":"فَإِن تَوَلَّوْا۟ فَإِنَّمَا عَلَيْكَ ٱلْبَلَٰغُ ٱلْمُبِينُ","translation":"BUT IF they turn away [from thee, O Prophet, remember that] thy only duty is a clear delivery of the message [entrusted to thee].","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1983.mp3","surahId":16,"words":[{"id":65015,"position":1,"arabic":"فَإِن","translation":"অতঃপর যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/016_082_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65016,"position":2,"arabic":"تَوَلَّوْا۟","translation":"তারা মুখ ফিরায়","audioUrl":"wbw/016_082_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65017,"position":3,"arabic":"فَإِنَّمَا","translation":"তবে কেবল","audioUrl":"wbw/016_082_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65018,"position":4,"arabic":"عَلَيْكَ","translation":"তোমার উপর দায়িত্ব","audioUrl":"wbw/016_082_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65019,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْبَلَـٰغُ","translation":"(দীনের দাওয়াত) পৌঁছানো","audioUrl":"wbw/016_082_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65020,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْمُبِينُ","translation":"সুস্পষ্টভাবে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_082_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65021,"position":7,"arabic":"٨٢","translation":"(৮২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":83,"arabic":"يَعْرِفُونَ نِعْمَتَ ٱللَّهِ ثُمَّ يُنكِرُونَهَا وَأَكْثَرُهُمُ ٱلْكَٰفِرُونَ","translation":"They [who turn away from it] are fully aware of God's blessings, but none the less they refuse to acknowledge them [as such], since most of them are given to denying the truth.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1984.mp3","surahId":16,"words":[{"id":65286,"position":1,"arabic":"يَعْرِفُونَ","translation":"তারা জানে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_083_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65287,"position":2,"arabic":"نِعْمَتَ","translation":"অনুগ্রহসমূহকে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_083_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65288,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/016_083_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65289,"position":4,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"এরপর","audioUrl":"wbw/016_083_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65290,"position":5,"arabic":"يُنكِرُونَهَا","translation":"তা তারা অস্বীকার করে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_083_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65291,"position":6,"arabic":"وَأَكْثَرُهُمُ","translation":"এবং তাদের অধিকাংশ","audioUrl":"wbw/016_083_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65292,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْكَـٰفِرُونَ","translation":"কাফের","audioUrl":"wbw/016_083_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65293,"position":8,"arabic":"٨٣","translation":"(৮৩)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":84,"arabic":"وَيَوْمَ نَبْعَثُ مِن كُلِّ أُمَّةٍۢ شَهِيدًۭا ثُمَّ لَا يُؤْذَنُ لِلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ وَلَا هُمْ يُسْتَعْتَبُونَ","translation":"But one Day We shall raise up a witness out of every community, whereupon they who were bent on denying the truth will not be allowed to plead [ignorance], and neither will they be allowed to make amends.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1985.mp3","surahId":16,"words":[{"id":65634,"position":1,"arabic":"وَيَوْمَ","translation":"এবং যেদিন","audioUrl":"wbw/016_084_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65635,"position":2,"arabic":"نَبْعَثُ","translation":"উত্থিত করবো আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/016_084_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65636,"position":3,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_084_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65637,"position":4,"arabic":"كُلِّ","translation":"প্রত্যেক","audioUrl":"wbw/016_084_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65638,"position":5,"arabic":"أُمَّةٍۢ","translation":"সম্প্রদায়","audioUrl":"wbw/016_084_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65639,"position":6,"arabic":"شَهِيدًۭا","translation":"সাক্ষী","audioUrl":"wbw/016_084_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65640,"position":7,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"এরপর","audioUrl":"wbw/016_084_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65641,"position":8,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/016_084_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65642,"position":9,"arabic":"يُؤْذَنُ","translation":"অনুমতি দেয়া হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_084_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65643,"position":10,"arabic":"لِلَّذِينَ","translation":"(তাদের) যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/016_084_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65644,"position":11,"arabic":"كَفَرُوا۟","translation":"অস্বীকার করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_084_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65645,"position":12,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/016_084_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65646,"position":13,"arabic":"هُمْ","translation":"তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/016_084_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65647,"position":14,"arabic":"يُسْتَعْتَبُونَ","translation":"সন্তুষ্টি লাভের সুযোগ দেয়া হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_084_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65648,"position":15,"arabic":"٨٤","translation":"(৮৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":85,"arabic":"وَإِذَا رَءَا ٱلَّذِينَ ظَلَمُوا۟ ٱلْعَذَابَ فَلَا يُخَفَّفُ عَنْهُمْ وَلَا هُمْ يُنظَرُونَ","translation":"And when they who were bent on evildoing behold the suffering [that awaits them, they will realize that] it will not be lightened for them [by virtue of their pleading]; and neither will they be granted respite.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1986.mp3","surahId":16,"words":[{"id":66000,"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","translation":"এবং যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/016_085_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":66001,"position":2,"arabic":"رَءَا","translation":"দেখবে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_085_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":66002,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/016_085_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":66003,"position":4,"arabic":"ظَلَمُوا۟","translation":"সীমালঙ্ঘন করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_085_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":66004,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْعَذَابَ","translation":"শাস্তি","audioUrl":"wbw/016_085_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":66005,"position":6,"arabic":"فَلَا","translation":"তখন না","audioUrl":"wbw/016_085_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":66006,"position":7,"arabic":"يُخَفَّفُ","translation":"লাঘব করা হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_085_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":66007,"position":8,"arabic":"عَنْهُمْ","translation":"তাদের থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_085_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":66008,"position":9,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/016_085_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":66009,"position":10,"arabic":"هُمْ","translation":"তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/016_085_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":66010,"position":11,"arabic":"يُنظَرُونَ","translation":"অবকাশ দেয়া হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_085_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":66011,"position":12,"arabic":"٨٥","translation":"(৮৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":86,"arabic":"وَإِذَا رَءَا ٱلَّذِينَ أَشْرَكُوا۟ شُرَكَآءَهُمْ قَالُوا۟ رَبَّنَا هَٰٓؤُلَآءِ شُرَكَآؤُنَا ٱلَّذِينَ كُنَّا نَدْعُوا۟ مِن دُونِكَ ۖ فَأَلْقَوْا۟ إِلَيْهِمُ ٱلْقَوْلَ إِنَّكُمْ لَكَٰذِبُونَ","translation":"And when they who were wont to ascribe divinity to beings other than God behold [on Judgment Day] those beings to whom they were wont to ascribe a share in His divinity, they will exclaim: \"O our Sustainer! These are the beings to whom we ascribed a share in Thy divinity, and whom we were wont to invoke instead of Thee!\" -whereupon [those beings] will fling at them the retort: \"Behold, you have indeed been lying [to yourselves]!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1987.mp3","surahId":16,"words":[{"id":66382,"po